title: Seattle City Council Briefing 5/26/2020
description:
In-person attendance is currently prohibited per the Washington Governor's Proclamation No. 20-28.2 until May 31, 2020. Meeting participation is limited to access by telephone conference line and Seattle Channel online.

Agenda: President's Report; Presentation on Council Bill 119799 - Premium Pay for Gig Workers; Preview of Today's City Council Actions, Council and Regional Committees.
